安雅·泰勒-乔伊在《Furiosa》中只有 30 句台词，连续“几个月”没有在片场发言https://www.nme.com/news/film/anya-taylor-joy-only-has-30-lines-of-dialogue-in-furiosa-went-months-without-speaking-on-set-3755963？ utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=anya-taylor-joy-only-has-30-lines-of-Dialogue-in-furiosa-goed-months-without-speaking-on-setSurej Singh Tue, 14 May 2024 08:20:27 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3755963 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/anya-taylor-joy@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/anya-taylor-joy@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/anya-taylor-joy@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/anya-taylor-joy@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/anya-taylor-joy@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/anya-taylor-joy@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/anya-taylor-joy@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>根据导演乔治·米勒的说法，对话“往往会放慢速度，而电影是一种通常最好在高速下欣赏的媒介”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/anya-taylor-joy-only-has-30-lines-of-dialogue-in-furiosa-went-months-without-speaking-on-set-3755963">安雅·泰勒-乔伊 (Anya Taylor-Joy) 在《Furiosa》中只有 30 句台词，“几个月”没有在片场讲话的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/anya-taylor-joy@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/anya-taylor-joy@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/anya-taylor-joy@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/anya-taylor-joy@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/anya-taylor-joy@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/anya-taylor-joy@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/anya-taylor-joy@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/furiosa"><em>《福瑞奥莎</em></a>》的主演<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/anya-taylor-joy">安雅·泰勒-乔伊</a>不会在即将上映的电影中发表太多言论 - 请在下文中了解原因。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-listid="5"><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-various-artists-16075-315225"><b>《疯狂的麦克斯：狂暴之路》——电影评论</b></a></li></ul><p>在最近接受<a href="https://www.telegraph.co.uk/films/2024/05/11/tom-hardy-george-miller-mad-max-furiosa-interview/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《电讯报》</em></a>采访时，导演乔治·米勒透露，饰演福瑞奥莎的泰勒-乔伊在整部电影中只有“大约”30 行对白。</p><p>据导演介绍，这是设计使然。 <em>《疯狂的麦克斯》</em>系列中的所有主演在他们的电影中都没有太多对话；<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mel-gibson">梅尔·吉布森</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-hardy">汤姆·哈迪</a>在各自的电影中都很少说话。米勒解释说，对话往往会减慢速度，而电影是一种最适合高速观看的媒介。相反，米勒依靠主演的面部反应和举止来讲述故事的能力。 </p><figure id="attachment_3754045" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3754045" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3754045" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Mad-Max-Furiosa.jpg" alt="福里奥萨" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Mad-Max-Furiosa.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Mad-Max-Furiosa-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Mad-Max-Furiosa-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Mad-Max-Furiosa-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Mad-Max-Furiosa-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Mad-Max-Furiosa-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3754045" class="wp-caption-text">安雅·泰勒-乔伊在《福瑞奥萨：疯狂的麦克斯传奇》中。图片来源：Jasin Boland/华纳兄弟</figcaption></figure><p>安雅·泰勒-乔伊在接受<a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2024/05/12/movies/anya-taylor-joy-furiosa.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《纽约时报》</em></a>采访时透露，台词数量极其有限，这意味着她“几个月”没有说过或录制一行对话。</p><p>然而，她表示，为了加入米勒最初反对的尖叫声，她“奋斗了三个月”。在解释米勒的方法时，泰勒-乔伊说：“他对弗瑞奥萨的战争面孔有一个非常非常严格的想法，这只让我能够看到电影的大部分内容。这就是“闭嘴​​，没有情感，用眼睛说话”。就是这样，这就是你所拥有的一切。”</p><p>她继续说道：“我是女性愤怒的坚定倡导者。我们都是动物，总有一天有人会发脾气。那部电影里有一声尖叫，当我告诉你我为那声尖叫奋斗了三个月时，我不是在开玩笑。对于乔治来说，这是一场漫长的比赛。” </p><figure id="attachment_3603611" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3603611" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3603611" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/furiosa_anya_taylorjoy.jpg" alt="《福瑞奥莎：疯狂的麦克斯传奇》" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/furiosa_anya_taylorjoy.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/furiosa_anya_taylorjoy-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/furiosa_anya_taylorjoy-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/furiosa_anya_taylorjoy-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/furiosa_anya_taylorjoy-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/furiosa_anya_taylorjoy-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3603611" class="wp-caption-text"> 《福瑞奥莎：疯狂的麦克斯传奇》。图片来源：华纳兄弟影业</figcaption></figure><p><em>《福瑞奥萨：疯狂的麦克斯传奇》</em>将于 3 月 23 日上映，已<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/furiosa-is-a-ferocious-prequel-to-mad-max-fury-road-say-critics-3754034">获得看过这部动作大片的影评人的好评</a>。 <a href="https://twitter.com/ErikDavis/status/1787656513789530128" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Fandango</em>的埃里克·戴维斯 (Erik Davis)</a>将这部电影描述为“一部凶猛且节奏紧凑的史诗，扩展了<em>福瑞奥萨</em>和荒原的故事，同时呈现了最疯狂的追逐、最夸张的角色和令人惊叹的摄影。”</p><p>这部电影由安雅·泰勒-乔伊和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chris-hemsworth">克里斯·海姆斯沃斯</a>主演，将作为 2015 年汤姆·哈迪、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charlize-theron">查理兹·塞隆</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/zo-kravitz">佐伊·克拉维茨</a>主演的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/best-film-past-25-years-rotten-tomatoes-3473276"><em>《疯狂的麦克斯：狂暴之路》</em></a>的前传。 </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/film/furiosa-is-a-ferocious-prequel-to-mad-max-fury-road-say-critics-3754034"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p>另据报道， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/furiosa-has-an-action-scene-that-took-78-days-to-film-3749217">上个月有消息称，</a> <em>《Furiosa》</em>中的一场动作戏拍摄耗时 78 天。</p></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/anya-taylor-joy-only-has-30-lines-of-dialogue-in-furiosa-went-months-without-speaking-on-set-3755963">安雅·泰勒-乔伊 (Anya Taylor-Joy) 在《Furiosa》中只有 30 句台词，“几个月”没有在片场讲话的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
在利亚姆称其“行为不当”后，诺尔·加拉格尔为没有在曼城的比赛中参加波兹南比赛进行辩护https://www.nme.com/news/noel-gallagher-defends-not-doing-poznan-at-man-city-game-after-liam-calls-out-poor-behaviour-3755945?utm_source=rss&utm_medium= rss&utm_campaign=诺埃尔·加拉格尔为在利亚姆呼吁不良行为后不参加波兹南曼城比赛辩护Tom SkinnerTue, 14 May 2024 07:40:05 +0000 Music NewsNewsBritpopIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3755945 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/NoelGallagher-defends-not-doing-Poznan-Man-City-game-.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="诺埃尔·加拉格尔" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/NoelGallagher-defends-not-doing-Poznan-Man-City-game-.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/NoelGallagher-defends-not-doing-Poznan-Man-City-game--400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/NoelGallagher-defends-not-doing-Poznan-Man-City-game--800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/NoelGallagher-defends-not-doing-Poznan-Man-City-game--696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/NoelGallagher-defends-not-doing-Poznan-Man-City-game--1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/NoelGallagher-defends-not-doing-Poznan-Man-City-game--1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位歌手兼作曲家将其归咎于“精彩的夜晚外出”后的宿醉</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/noel-gallagher-defends-not-doing-poznan-at-man-city-game-after-liam-calls-out-poor-behaviour-3755945">在利亚姆指责“不良行为”后，诺埃尔·加拉格尔为没有在曼城的比赛中参加波兹南比赛辩护的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/NoelGallagher-defends-not-doing-Poznan-Man-City-game-.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="诺埃尔·加拉格尔" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/NoelGallagher-defends-not-doing-Poznan-Man-City-game-.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/NoelGallagher-defends-not-doing-Poznan-Man-City-game--400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/NoelGallagher-defends-not-doing-Poznan-Man-City-game--800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/NoelGallagher-defends-not-doing-Poznan-Man-City-game--696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/NoelGallagher-defends-not-doing-Poznan-Man-City-game--1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/NoelGallagher-defends-not-doing-Poznan-Man-City-game--1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallagher">诺尔·加拉格尔</a>为上周末曼城对阵富勒姆的比赛中没有随波兹南队一起参加比赛进行了辩护，他的兄弟<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">利亚姆</a>称其为“糟糕的行为”。</p><p>这位前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">绿洲</a>成员观看了上周六（5 月 11 日）的客场比赛，他心爱的球队以 4-0 获胜，距离英超积分榜榜首更近了一步。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/noel-gallagher-interview-oasis-council-skies-3451058">诺埃尔·加拉格尔（Noel Gallagher）：“世界是一个美丽的地方——只是居住着混蛋”</a></strong></li></ul><div id="playlist-player-jwplayer"><div class="playlist-player-container"><p>但与包围他的曼城球迷的海洋不同的是， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-noel-gallagher-refuse-to-do-the-poznan-in-sea-of-celebrating-man-city-fans-3755532">加拉格尔拒绝加入波兹南</a>（球迷们挽着手，转身离开球场并开始弹跳）。</p><p>随后，这一时刻的图片和视频迅速疯传，一些人表示，看上去不为所动的加拉格尔可能正在为他的下一张专辑拍摄封面艺术。</p><p>这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallaghers-high-flying-birds">High Flying Birds</a>主唱的关系疏远的兄弟、前乐队成员 Liam 也在 X/Twitter 上发帖称其“行为恶劣”。</p><p>此后，诺埃尔在接受<a href="https://talksport.com/football/1864637/noel-gallagher-poznan-manchester-city-fulham/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>talkSport</em></a>采访时谈到了自己在比赛中被发现的事情。 “直到你离开地面并且手机爆炸时你才真正知道，”他解释道。</p><p> “我不得不说，周六我仍然感受到了一个相当精彩的夜晚的影响。”</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">不良行为</p><p>— 利亚姆·加拉格尔 (@liamgallagher) <a href="https://twitter.com/liamgallagher/status/1789300039916945684?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 5 月 11 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="诺埃尔·加拉格尔因严重宿醉而拒绝与曼城球迷一起参加波兹南庆祝活动！ 🤢😅" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/63dtRffTnx4?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>诺埃尔继续说道：“所以即使我想加入波兹南，我也不认为我能够做到！”</p><p>然而，有人看到这位音乐家在人群中挥舞拳头庆祝菲尔·福登帮助曼城2-0领先的进球。</p><p>在采访的其他地方，诺埃尔被问到支持曼城这样的统治球队是否有任何危险。</p><p>他回答道：“我认为会有一部分球迷不紧张，但和我一起去的人来自不同的时代，所以我们总是会紧张。</p><p> “我们为这支球队提供了大约 50 年的支持，但年轻一代认为我们会坚持下去，仅此而已。”</p><p>您可以在上面的视频中查看完整的采访。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Noel Gallagher 谈“议会天空”、人工智能绿洲、1975 年和英国脱欧" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/qUl5BVqtNZU?start=43&#038;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在其他新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-says-he-has-scrapped-acoustic-album-and-wants-to-do-a-defiant-rock-record-3613651">诺埃尔·加拉格尔最近透露，他已经“取消”了计划中的原声专辑</a>。他解释说，这些材料“太低级”，并补充道：“我需要制作一张挑衅性的摇滚唱片，这就是我要做的。” </p><div class="advert-wrapper advert-wrapper--articlempu"><div id="articlempu" class="dfp-ad advert--inarticle"><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-noel-gallagher-refuse-to-do-the-poznan-in-sea-of-celebrating-man-city-fans-3755532">这位歌手兼词曲作者上周在伦敦 O2 Academy Brixton 的舞台上与 The Black Keys 一起现场演出</a>，此前他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-says-songs-hes-co-written-with-the-black-keys-are-fucking-amazing-3455959">为二人组的最新专辑《Ohio Players》做出了贡献</a>。</p><p>与此同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-oasis-definitely-mayb